Meh I’m sad that @starsonice is not going on tour in October, so now I’m looking for a hobby. Also, I was finally starting to feel like I was getting my legs back under me so I need some motivation. 

Also, this song, dancing on my own, was the first song I danced to in a genre that wasn’t ballet and boy, did I hide in the back of the classroom…which is so funny because I don’t hide on the ice. Anyone else feel the same? 

#dancingonmyown

node.text:
Did you know that “Don’t Stop Me Now” induces happiness regularly?

I loved this song when I was a teen and after a little bit of research, I found out that I’m not the only one! ♥️😎

#happy #happysong #queen #dontstopmenow #iceskater #iceskate #skate #skater #figureskate #figureskater #music #musicismylife #freddiemercury

node.text:
Casual reminder to give yourself breaks from working, and the Boston lights were lit 🔥

….also, I jumped into the @crocs family and I’m never looking back. #jibbitz needed soon. 🥰
